假如dy/dx真的等如dy除以dx的話，會導致以下結果
let y(x) = 0, then dy/dx = 0 for all x. In order dy/dx to be well-defined, dx =/= 0 under all circumstances. In order to have consistent symbol, dy =/=0 under all circumstances, too. But dy/dx = 0 => dy = 0 * dx = 0 => dy = 0, contradicting the consistency of symbol.

